Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io This package contains the BPEL reader and writer interfaces and the factory classes to access them. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers This package contains the default impl of the IAeBpelReader interface.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.registry This package contains the registry classes for accessing readers and writers for BPEL and extension elements.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers This package provides the impl classes for the IAeBpelWriter interface.
